1 tomato
1 cucumber
1 packet sweet chilli sauce
1 packet beef strips
1 sachet Sweet Soy Seasoning
1 bag Mixed Salad Leaves
1 packet roasted peanuts
1 packet garlic aioli
1 packet Roasted Pumpkin
olive oil

• Prick a few holes in pumpkin
packet. Microwave until hot and
steaming, 3 mins
• Chop tomato. Thinly slice
cucumber
• In a bowl, combine sweet chilli
sauce and a drizzle of olive oil

• Heat oil in a frying pan over
high heat
• Cook beef and sweet soy
seasoning, tossing, until browned,
1-2 mins

• Add tomato, cucumber and mixed
salad leaves to sweet chilli dressing.
Season and toss
• Plate up salad and pumpkin. Top
with beef and peanuts
• Serve with garlic aioli